        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "In version 1.10.x\r\n{code:title=class Zend_Form_Element|borderStyle=solid}\r\npublic function getLabel()\r\n{\r\n    $translator = $this->getTranslator();\r\n    if (null !== $translator) {\r\n        return $translator->translate($this->_label);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    return $this->_label;\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nIt cause problem, because the translation is running twice.\r\n1. When calling getLabel()\r\n2. And the Translate adapter globaly \r\n\r\nBefore version 1.10.x worked fine.\r\n{code}\r\npublic function getLabel()\r\n{\r\n    return $this->_label;\r\n}\r\n{code} "
        },
