                    },
                    "body": "Updated title to reflect that this issue is a parent of SubTasks now.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-03T05:22:05.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-03T05:22:05.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/40750",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "After reading through the Sub Tasks, older issues and most important\r\nthe [Zend_Form-2.0 wiki|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/wiki\/display\/ZFDEV2\/Zend_Form+2.0#Zend_Form2.0-Translation], i will move all translate calls from \r\nZend_Form and Zend_Form_Element_* into Zend_Form_Decorator_*\r\n\/\/ edit\r\nand into Zend_View_Helper_Form* according to where the final rendering occurs,\r\nin a way that the original Element attributes won't be translated.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-05-28T05:44:49.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-05-28T06:44:09.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41028",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "We had a discussion in irc where wwe thought about implementing \r\na Decorator_Translate to do all the translations for configured\r\nattribs and\/or values. http:\/\/zftalk.com\/logs\/view\/zftalk.dev\/2010\/06\/03\/\r\n\r\nAny Comments?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-17T13:02:00.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-17T13:02:00.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41121",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This may be a good idea or not, but it looks like a long term solution to me. For the moment, I'd be more than happy to see the fixes (which have been around for months and work flawlessly) finally make it into a release. It's really annoying to apply them after every update.\r\n\r\nIs there any good reason why this has not been addressed yet?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-20T11:42:25.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-20T11:42:25.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41242",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=johndoe",
                        "name": "johndoe",
                        "displayName": "Ren\u00e9 Kerner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "vice versa linked...",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=johndoe",
                        "name": "johndoe",
                        "displayName": "Ren\u00e9 Kerner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-29T04:50:14.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-29T04:50:14.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41279",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Holger which fixes are you refering to?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-06-30T14:41:47.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-06-30T14:41:47.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/41315",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "One of the fixes (including tests) is attached to ZF-8764. I can't find the other one ATM (already too many open bug reports about this). I have attached a patch that fixes both issues (without the tests).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hschletz",
                        "name": "hschletz",
                        "displayName": "Holger Schletz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-07-04T07:30:41.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-07-04T07:30:41.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/44395",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=g.schuster",
                        "name": "g.schuster",
                        "displayName": "Gabriel Schuster",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "2011 and still no fix for this...\r\nCan it really be true that there's no committer that is willing to apply a patch?\r\nWhy not just fix it to prevent translate-logs filling with garbage and developing cool things like Decorator_Translate later?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=g.schuster",
                        "name": "g.schuster",
                        "displayName": "Gabriel Schuster",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-02-16T14:49:12.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-02-16T14:49:12.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/44397",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kaiuwe",
                        "name": "kaiuwe",
                        "displayName": "Kai Uwe",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "??developing cool things like Decorator_Translate??\r\n\r\n[Zend_Form 2.0 - Recommendations: Translation|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/wiki\/display\/ZFDEV2\/Zend_Form+2.0#Zend_Form2.0-Translation]\r\n\r\n{quote}\r\nTranslation should be moved to the view layer. The View and Decorator chains would receive the Translator object and use it to translate appropriate labels and metadata. As such, the form, its elements, and the individual validator and validator chains would need no such knowledge of this information.\r\n{quote}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kaiuwe",
                        "name": "kaiuwe",
                        "displayName": "Kai Uwe",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-02-17T00:10:14.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-02-17T00:10:14.000+0000"
                },
